span style=\"color: red;\">女事主有情緒病紀錄</span>。"},{"pid":"c048082909122fc51d6e8f2bcdc7504155210a8c","tid":516309,"uid":147871,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3a1b6d093e2dc5d1365bef237502d58a024f4e4f","tid":516309,"uid":19725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T09:57:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咩人自殺前會冇情緒問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nConfounding <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T09:58:41.000Z","msg":"咁咩人比例尋死會多d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d26d6cbee29cce8ed6163b7a6c731494a4c23ff","tid":516309,"uid":42188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T09:59:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咩人自殺前會冇情緒問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我講緊情緒病記錄<br />\n唔係單純唔開心既情緒問題"},{"pid":"a79454a7d0f8245ea794bb3e3f72b6636249c8e4","tid":516309,"uid":147871,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5d26d6cbee29cce8ed6163b7a6c731494a4c23ff","tid":516309,"uid":42188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T09:59:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咩人自殺前會冇情緒問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我講緊情緒病記錄<br />\n唔係單純唔開心既情緒問題"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T10:00:32.000Z","msg":"冇去睇醫生姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ebd788eeceb3e6ad48b92ec4ac75e5a2efdbd5ab","tid":516309,"uid":42188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T10:02:14.000Z","msg":"2017-09-24<br />\n富亨邨34歲IT男墮樓分屍　親友認屍哭崩<br />\n<br />\n警方未檢獲遺書，初步認為無可疑，正調查其墮樓原因。據悉，梁任職資訊科技工作，<span style=\"color: red;\">有情緒病記錄</span>，不排除他因病發從大廈梯間跳樓輕生。"},{"pid":"38ea720ec9da5d4f54426a140fbcfe8d1a16ab0e","tid":516309,"uid":57566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T10:03:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>咩人自殺前會冇情